title: Hour 3 - Aaron Judge Stuck on 60, Clay Matthews
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Aaron Judge Stuck on 60, Clay Matthews
description:
Dan feels bad for the Maris family while they chase Aaron Judge around the league as he tries to match Roger Maris' American League HR record. And Clay Matthews drops in and refuses to consider himself retired (wink, wink) since he only needs a few sacks to get to 100 in his career.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
